{3: 'Lee and Liv are protecting the watermelon from the evil that is Nanami. Nanami is off to one side, staring at the watermelon and sulking.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Lee, you might turn out to be a good competitive swimmer.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Because you look good in a swimsuit.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Liv nods in agreement.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "I never imagined you in a swimsuit before, Lee, but after I actually saw you in one, it feels like you're made to wear it.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "But you can't swim, right, Lee...?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'If there are water-based operations in the future, I will install the appropriate modules.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'So what should we play next? Is there anything you want to play, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Leave it to Nanami! Nanami knows everything about play!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami has been researching human behavior, and I know everything about beach sports!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "First, Liv, you'll have to sit here, like this!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Then Commandant, you have to lie on Liv's lap.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Stop messing around.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Aww, well... Then we can bury Commandant in sand, and make a sand castle on top.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't think this game supports that.", 4: '2'}
{2: "So does this mean you'll do it, if it's possible?", 3: '35'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Don't put words in my mouth.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hmmmmmm, well then...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Where are you getting all these weird ideas from...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'In old human shows, the beach episode is almost always episode 7 or 8 in the series! Nanami has figured out the pattern!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami got through all of it in the database, which makes Nanami a beach master!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't know what you're talking about, but you should stop watching those weird shows.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Your towel is falling off.', 3: '43'}
{3: "You reach over to grab the towel falling off Lee's body, but your hand slips right through his shoulder."}
{3: '...Right. This is a virtual space.'}
{3: 'You withdraw your hand awkwardly.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'It would be great if we could all come to a real beach to play like this.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'The Corrupted are everywhere on Earth. We will have to find a suitable beach and cleanse the area first, then section off a safe zone.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't think our superiors would be so kind as to let us go down to earth simply for entertainment.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "But I guess... inside a game like this, there's no need to worry about the Corrupted, at least.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Oh... There are no Corrupted here, but...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Booms resound in the distance. It closes in by the second.'}
{3: 'Spurts of sand fly up on the beach. The sound grows louder.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "But if it's just normal baddies! There's a bunch of 'em!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The source of the noise reveals itself to be a group of mechanoids, charging over at you.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'These are simulated enemies used in training! Why would their data be in this game?!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Ehehe! You can thank Nanami for that!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'But why even Musashi models on the beach?', 3: '69'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Because Nanami thinks Musashi might also want a beach vacation.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Don't just mod in whatever you want!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'But Nanami wants to play Tsar Cry!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Hahaha! Isn't this fun? We can just treat it like an action game!", 4: '1'}
